{
  "text": "In the Distributed Video Coding based on the theory of information coding presented by Slepian, Wolf, Wyner and Ziv in the seventies of last century [CITATION_1] , we run independently the coding work at the coding end and run the joint decoding work at the decoding end according to the relativity of the time domain and the space domain of The research of the distributed compressive sensing is divided into the research of the sparse representation algorithm of the coding end, the research of the reconstruction algorithm of the decoding end and the research of the transmission strategy in the transmission process. We don't consider the influence of the sparse representation algorithm and the reconstruction algorithm in this article. We study the influence of the quantization method in this article and design and achieve the new quantization matrix adapting to the distributed compressive sensing video coding.",
  "citation_candidates": [
